<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Accepted</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Congratulations, <%= first_name %> <%= last_name %>!</h1>

    <p>We are pleased to inform you that your application for the <strong><%= job_title %></strong> position at <strong><%= job_company %></strong> has been accepted.</p>

    <p>We will be in touch soon with further details regarding the next steps.</p>
    
    <p>We look forward to working with you!</p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The <%= job_company %> Team</p>
</body>
</html>
